【UNSCENTED & ODORLESS TRASH BAGS】These Are Unscented,Non-Toxic And Pure. It Controls The Odor Very Well, And Help Us Identify The Contents Of The Garbage So That Sorting And Recycling Of It Better.
【2.6 - 4 GALLON TRASH BAGS】Size 19 in x 19 in. Fits most small round trash cans in size within 10.0 in x 17.0 in and square trash bins whose perimiter and high within 33.0 in x 17.0 in.

【TEAR RESISTANT DRAWSTING TRASH BAGS】Point break connecting with constant temperature sealing, easy to get bags separate without tearing. Comes with hidden vents and effectively prevent bursting. No need to worry about dropping garbage in your house because of bursting accident.

【SEAL BOTTOM】Allows even weight distribution and easy removal from receptacle. It also helps to eliminate leaks, messes and spills and make trash disposal much easier. This bag is translucent or semi-clear. It allows to easily view and identify the contents of the bag to help separate recyclable from non-recyclable materials.
description: Reducing the use and promoting recycling is not the fundamental way to solve,we need to completely replace the traditional plastic bag.Our mission is to achieve sustainable development. For garbage bags,biodegradability is the best choice!
Perfectly Sized for Use Throughout the Home
Small Trash Bags are ideal for home, offices, nurseries and even on-the-go. You can use it in many places.
Our small trash bags are made of Eco PE material, which is health and safety, no smell, can be used with confidence, fit most of small size trash bins.
We used the breaking design to avoid breaking the next trash bag. Only need to tear the bag off easily and then you can get a trash bag without breaking the next one.
The sealed bottom doesn’t leave any space to leak. And making it easier to remove the bag from the trash box.
